{"id":34717,"date":"2022-11-23T13:19:36","date_gmt":"2022-11-23T21:19:36","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/?page_id=34717"},"modified":"2025-11-25T17:41:53","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T22:41:53","slug":"high-performance-digital-advertising","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/high-performance-digital-advertising\/","title":{"rendered":"High Performance Digital Advertising"},"content":{"rendered":"\r\n<h1>High Performance Digital Advertising<\/h1>\r\n<p>Nowspeed creates and manages winning Google <a href=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/ppc\/\">PPC<\/a>, Microsoft Bing, LinkedIn, Facebook, Instagram and Twitter Ad campaigns. Ask us about a complimentary audit of your account to see how much more effective your campaigns can be!<\/p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/free-digital-marketing-audit\/\" target=\"_self\"> FREE AUDIT <\/a><\/p>\r\n<h2>Free 15-Point Digital Advertising Audit!<\/h2>\r\n<p>Do you want to find out how to create a winning digital advertising program? Fill out the form to schedule your free audit.<\/p>\r\n<p>For qualified companies, we will review your <a href=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/ppc\/\">PPC<\/a> strategy, dig into your campaign structure, look under the hood at your keywords, and review a dozen other factors that impact the success of your campaigns. This audit will identify key issues and help us both understand how we can improve your results.<\/p>\r\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" title=\"Computer-Screen-Marketing (1)\" src=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Computer-Screen-Marketing-1.png\" alt=\"Digital Advertising\" width=\"1162\" height=\"907\" \/><\/p>\r\n<h2>High Performance Digital Advertising<\/h2>\r\n<p>Nowspeed creates and manages integrated digital advertising campaigns that drive profitable results for clients in many industries. Our strategic approach, comprehensive analytics, talented staff, and powerful methodology allow us to supercharge your campaigns. We&#8217;ve managed over $150MM in ad budget and have a track record of improving results by more than 50% for many clients.<\/p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/free-digital-marketing-audit\/\" target=\"_self\"> Free Audit and 90 Day Digital Ad Roadmap <\/a><\/p>\r\n<h2>We lead with Experience and Validate with Data<\/h2>\r\n<p>We start every new client relationship with a deep dive into all aspects of your ad campaigns. We&#8217;ll review your strategy, look under the hood at your campaign analytics and settings, and dig deep into your budget allocation, content, offers, landing pages, ad messages and competitors. The audit and 90 Day Plan we provide will make it clear that we can improve your results.<\/p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/free-digital-marketing-audit\/\" target=\"_self\"> FREE AUDIT <\/a> <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" title=\"Validate with Data\" src=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Image-2.jpg\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 950px) 100vw, 950px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Image-2.jpg 950w, https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Image-2-300x257.jpg 300w, https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Image-2-768x659.jpg 768w\" alt=\"Experience and Validate with Data\" width=\"950\" height=\"815\" \/><\/p>\r\n<p>\u201cWe had a great relationship with Nowspeed. It has been very thorough, very positive, and in depth\u2026 \u201c<\/p>\r\n<p>&#8211; RedWave Technology <a href=\"\/our-work\/client-testimonials\/\"> Read More \u00bb<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>\u201cWow! We are blown away by the new Provision website. Such a huge transformation! I really believe we now have a site that effectively\u2026\u201d<\/p>\r\n<p>&#8211; Provision <a href=\"\/our-work\/client-testimonials\/\"> Read More \u00bb<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>\u201cWorking with Max and Joseph on our Nowspeed team has been a great experience. I have been involved in marketing\u2026\u201d<\/p>\r\n<p>&#8211; Collins, Ritchie, &amp; Ervin <a href=\"\/our-work\/client-testimonials\/\"> Read More \u00bb<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>\u201cNowspeed is an extension of our marketing team and has assisted in development, tracking and analysis\u2026\u201d<\/p>\r\n<p>&#8211; Wiese USA <a href=\"\/our-work\/client-testimonials\/\"> Read More \u00bb<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>\u201cWorking with Nowspeed to support our organic and paid social media activity has extended the marketing activities\u2026\u201d<\/p>\r\n<p>&#8211; Onset Computer Corp <a href=\"\/our-work\/client-testimonials\/\"> Read More \u00bb<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>\u201cThe Nowspeed team has helped turn our SEO around and we are finally seeing positive results. They serves as an extension\u2026\u201d<\/p>\r\n<p>&#8211; Cambridge Technology <a href=\"\/our-work\/client-testimonials\/\"> Read More \u00bb<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>\u201cFirst and foremost, Nowspeed\u2019s SEO and PPC work on our behalf has translated into meaningful visibility and lead\u2026\u201d<\/p>\r\n<p>&#8211; Cambrian Innovation <a href=\"\/our-work\/client-testimonials\/\"> Read More \u00bb<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>\u201cEveryone at Nowspeed that I&#8217;ve met has been extremely helpful, using their experience to silence the distractions\u2026\u201d<\/p>\r\n<p>&#8211; A2B Tracking <a href=\"\/our-work\/client-testimonials\/\"> Read More \u00bb<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>\u201cOutside GC relies on Nowspeed for its digital marketing expertise, particularly in the areas of SEO and social\u2026\u201d<\/p>\r\n<p>&#8211; Outside GC <a href=\"\/our-work\/client-testimonials\/\"> Read More \u00bb<\/a><\/p>\r\n<p>&#8220;The Nowspeed team provides Formation Data Systems with a full service digital marketing service that encompasses\u2026\u201d<\/p>\r\n<p>&#8211; Formation Data Systems <a href=\"\/our-work\/client-testimonials\/\"> Read More \u00bb<\/a><\/p>\r\n<!-- .pp-content-posts -->\r\n<h2>DIGITAL MARKETING EXPERTS WITH UNMATCHED KNOWLEDGE AND ATTENTION TO DETAIL.<\/h2>\r\n<p>With the experienced Nowspeed team at your side, your campaigns will be bui